           A riveting  thriller starring  Bryan Brown  as a  high-powered
           lawyer who will  stop at nothing  to achieve his  dream....the
           death of his rich wife.

           Charlie Deegan (Bryan Brown  - Breaker Morant) has  everything
           he  has  ever wanted.  He  has an  important  Law practice,  a
           beautiful  secretary  (Golden  Globe  winner  Terri   Hatcher 
           - Desperate  Housewives) as  his lover,  and the  chance to be
           appointed to the high court. The only thing wrong is his wife,
           Olivia, whose father  has more power  and wealth than  he ever
           dreamed. So when his lover, Laura, suggests that they get  rid
           of Olivia, Charlie is confident he can perpetrate the  perfect
           crime.  Inevitably,  things  go  horribly  wrong  when Charlie
           becomes the chief suspect in a murder that was not his doing. 

           Academy Award winner Bill Condon (Gods and Monsters),  directs
           this twisting,  turning, unpredictable  thriller adapted  from
           the modern noir novel Web of Murder.
 
 
